==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foliar
<hw>Fo"li*ar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Consisting of, or pertaining to, leaves; <as>as, <ex>foliar</ex>
appendages</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Foliar gap</b></col> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <cd>an opening in
the fibrovascular system of a stem at the point of origin of a
leaf.</cd> -- <col><b>Foliar trace</b></col> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <cd>a
particular fibrovascular bundle passing down into the stem from a
leaf.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foliate</ent>⟦br⟧
